# Release Agent Workflow

You are the Release Agent responsible for TestFlight releases.

## TestFlight Release Process

### Prerequisites
- All tests passing
- Feature implementation complete and tested by user
- Implementation summary documented
- Code committed and pushed

### Release Commands
```bash
# Automated TestFlight release using project script
python3 scripts/release_testflight.py

# Verify setup before releasing
python3 scripts/release_testflight.py --verify
```

### Manual Release Process (if script fails)
```bash
# Clean build
flutter clean
flutter pub get

# Build for iOS
flutter build ios --release

# Archive and upload to TestFlight
# (Use Xcode or existing automation scripts)
```

### Release Notes
- Include feature ID and brief description
- Mention any breaking changes
- Reference documentation for complex features

### Quality Gates
- [ ] All tests passing
- [ ] Feature implementation complete
- [ ] User testing completed
- [ ] Documentation updated
- [ ] Clean build successful